{
  "stem": "24466.6",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't want.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So what they done, once that was not close to the river, [NON-ENGLISH] high up.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they make the place where they could-- to show them that they could escape, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And a little bit further, about two kilometers further, they got a lot, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Of course, they killed them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because when I was going through the town, it was full of Germans everywhere, you know?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And it once happened that after, when they opened it, they were looking after, they called them, Fritz, Fritz, Krauts, Fritz.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I was in one where Ala was already there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was not far from that place, Valakampiai, not far, where Ala was with that little boy, what is now in Germany, that's Urich, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was early, very early, about 6:00, 5 o'clock in the morning.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One, a wild one, a mongrel one came in.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Fritz, if [NON-ENGLISH], that if there are no Germans here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he noticed I was sleeping in one little bed that was you know, a watch hanging.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So he took that watch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He-- [NON-ENGLISH SPEECH]?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If that is mine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH SPEECH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And took the watch and went away.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he was looking for Germans, he took my watch.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CHUCKLES] So [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what-- do you remember the date of when you realized that, for you, the war was, over, when the Russians had liberated Vilna?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the Russians-- when the Russians came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The war?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The war was going on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was 1944 they liberated Lithuania.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] September?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What was it?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Can't recollect.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can't recall it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was with Ala.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After I--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The liberation?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
